offsets -> PoolStats.fields
PoolStats.fields -> sizes
legend: {
  near: bottom-center
  style.fill: transparent
  desc: |md
    **Field Descriptions:**
    - `total_blocks`: Total capacity across all chunks
    - `allocated`: Blocks currently in use
    - `free`: Available blocks (calculated: total - allocated)
    - `chunk_count`: Number of memory chunks allocated
    - `block_size`: Aligned bytes per block
    - `total_bytes`: block_size × total_capacity
    - `overhead_bytes`: Chunk metadata + bitmap size
  |
}